m de semana, eu não trabalho.", "boundaries": [{"text": "No ", "start": 96.413, "end": 96.529}, {"text": "fim ", "start": 96.576, "end": 96.715}, {"text": "de ", "start": 96.75, "end": 96.808}, {"text": "semana, ", "start": 96.854, "end": 97.354}, {"text": "eu ", "start": 97.447, "end": 97.574}, {"text": "não", "start": 97.609, "end": 97.714}]}, {"id": "p5s2", "text": "No sábado de manhã, eu vou ao parque com o meu cachorro e a minha irmã.", "boundaries": [{"text": "o ", "start": 98.875, "end": 98.91}, {"text": "computador ", "start": 98.956, "end": 99.572}, {"text": "por ", "start": 99.641, "end": 99.815}, {"text": "uma ", "start": 99.908, "end": 100.129}, {"text": "hora. ", "start": 100.152, "end": 100.675}, {"text": "No ", "start": 101.267, "end": 101.383}, {"text": "fim ", "start": 101.441, "end": 101.615}, {"text": "de ", "start": 101.661, "end": 101.719}, {"text": "semana, ", "start": 101.777, "end": 102.323}, {"text": "eu ", "start": 102.393, "end": 102.532}, {"text": "não ", "start": 102.59, "end": 102.706}, {"text": "trabalho. ", "start": 102.741, "end": 103.438}, {"text": "nha", "start": 103.67, "end": 103.763}]}, {"id": "p5s3", "text": "Nós caminhamos muito e o cachorro corre.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nós ", "start": 104.889, "end": 105.109}, {"text": "caminhamos ", "start": 105.167, "end": 105.713}, {"text": "muito ", "start": 105.783, "end": 106.282}, {"text": "e ", "start": 106.456, "end": 106.572}, {"text": "o ", "start": 106.619, "end": 106.654}, {"text": "cachorro", "start": 106.688, "end": 107.153}]}, {"id": "p5s4", "text": "À tarde, eu visito o meu amigo Pedro.", "boundaries": [{"text": "À ", "start": 108.372, "end": 108.453}, {"text": "tarde, ", "start": 108.569, "end": 109.022}, {"text": "eu ", "start": 109.057, "end": 109.196}, {"text": "visito ", "start": 109.254, "end": 109.661}, {"text": "o ", "start": 109.684, "end": 109.707}, {"text": "meu ", "start": 109.765, "end": 109.904}, {"text": "amigo", "start": 109.951, "end": 110.206}]}, {"id": "p5s5", "text": "No domingo, eu descanso em casa com a minha família.", "boundaries": [{"text": "No ", "start": 111.379, "end": 111.506}, {"text": "domingo, ", "start": 111.553, "end": 112.122}, {"text": "eu ", "start": 112.157, "end": 112.308}, {"text": "descanso ", "start": 112.354, "end": 112.807}, {"text": "em ", "start": 112.842, "end": 112.9}, {"text": "casa ", "start": 112.958, "end": 113.272}, {"text": "com ", "start": 113.306, "end": 113.446}, {"text": "a ", "start": 113.481, "end": 113.504}, {"text": "minha", "start": 113.539, "end": 113.713}]}, {"id": "p5s6", "text": "Nós almoçamos frango com batatas juntos.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nós ", "start": 115.184, "end": 115.416}, {"text": "almoçamos ", "start": 115.463, "end": 115.939}, {"text": "frango ", "start": 116.008, "end": 116.322}, {"text": "com ", "start": 116.357, "end": 116.461}, {"text": "batatas", "start": 116.496, "end": 116.984}]}, {"id": "p5s7", "text": "Nós conversamos muito.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nós ", "start": 118.191, "end": 118.342}, {"text": "conversamos", "start": 118.388, "end": 118.957}]}, {"id": "p5s8", "text": "É uma vida simples, mas eu sou muito feliz.", "boundaries": [{"text": "É ", "start": 120.13, "end": 120.223}, {"text": "uma ", "start": 120.269, "end": 120.374}, {"text": "vida ", "start": 120.408, "end": 120.617}, {"text": "simples, ", "start": 120.676, "end": 121.244}, {"text": "mas ", "start": 121.569, "end": 121.72}, {"text": "eu ", "start": 121.767, "end": 121.813}, {"text": "sou ", "start": 121.848, "end": 121.999}, {"text": "muito", "start": 122.057, "end": 122.336}]}]}]}